00:52:33,400 --> 00:52:35,600
Tolong tinggalkan kantor sebentar.

715
00:52:35,600 --> 00:52:36,440
Baik.

716
00:52:37,670 --> 00:52:38,570
Cepat, cepat.

717
00:52:42,310 --> 00:52:43,810
Aku bisa gila.

